Package game.Capability

Enum Status

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Status>
game.Capability.Status
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Status>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum Status
extends java.lang.Enum<Status>
A generic collection of enums which represents states in which objects and actors may be in. These constants can be used as capabilities to avoid downcasting
